{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":703,"text":"Today,"},{"time":2684,"text":"a baffled lady observed"},{"time":4324,"text":"the shell where my soul dwells"}]},{"cues":[{"time":6316,"text":"And announced that I'm"},{"time":9457,"text":"\"articulate\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":11364,"text":"Which means that when it comes"},{"time":13702,"text":"to enunciation and diction"}]},{"cues":[{"time":15697,"text":"I don't even think of it"}]},{"cues":[{"time":16703,"text":"‘Cause I’m \"articulate\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":19390,"text":"So when my professor asks a question"}]},{"cues":[{"time":21970,"text":"And my answer is tainted with a connotation"},{"time":24129,"text":"of urbanized suggestion"}]},{"cues":[{"time":25477,"text":"There’s no misdirected intention"}]},{"cues":[{"time":27943,"text":"Pay attention"}]},{"cues":[{"time":28920,"text":"‘Cause I’m “articulate”"}]},{"cues":[{"time":31258,"text":"So when my father asks, “Wha’ kinda ting is dis?”"}]},{"cues":[{"time":34815,"text":"My “articulate” answer never goes amiss"}]},{"cues":[{"time":37953,"text":"I say “father, this is the impending problem at hand”"}]},{"cues":[{"time":41469,"text":"And when I’m on the block"},{"time":42796,"text":"I switch it up just because I can"}]},{"cues":[{"time":44491,"text":"So when my boy says, “What’s good with you son?”"}]},{"cues":[{"time":47129,"text":"I just say, “I jus’ fall out wit dem people but I done!”"}]},{"cues":[{"time":52539,"text":"And sometimes in class"}]},{"cues":[{"time":54131,"text":"I might pause the intellectual sounding flow to ask"}]},{"cues":[{"time":57060,"text":"“Yo! Why dese books neva be about my peoples”"}]},{"cues":[{"time":60725,"text":"Yes, I have decided to treat"},{"time":62890,"text":"all three of my languages as equals"}]},{"cues":[{"time":64952,"text":"Because I’m “articulate”"}]},{"cues":[{"time":68950,"text":"But who controls articulation?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":71371,"text":"Because the English language\nis a multifaceted oration"}]},{"cues":[{"time":74525,"text":"Subject to indefinite transformation"}]},{"cues":[{"time":76344,"text":"Now you may think that it is\nignorant to speak broken English"}]},{"cues":[{"time":79957,"text":"But I’m here to tell you that\neven “articulate” Americans"},{"time":83114,"text":"sound foolish to the British"}]},{"cues":[{"time":85114,"text":"So when my Professor comes on\nthe block and says, “Hello”"}]},{"cues":[{"time":88363,"text":"I stop him and say “Noooo …"}]},{"cues":[{"time":91000,"text":"You’re being inarticulate …"},{"time":93144,"text":"the proper way is to say ‘what’s good’”"}]},{"cues":[{"time":95307,"text":"Now you may think that’s too hood, that’s not cool"}]},{"cues":[{"time":98922,"text":"But I’m here to tell you that\neven our language has rules\n"}]},{"cues":[{"time":101900,"text":"So when Mommy mocks me and says"},{"time":104512,"text":"“ya’ll-be-madd-going-to-the-store”"}]},{"cues":[{"time":106770,"text":"I say “Mommy, no, that sentence is not following the law"}]},{"cues":[{"time":111756,"text":"Never does the word \"madd\" go \nbefore a present participle"}]},{"cues":[{"time":115447,"text":"That’s simply the principle of this English”"}]},{"cues":[{"time":117950,"text":"If I had the vocal capacity I would"},{"time":119620,"text":"sing this from every mountaintop,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":121674,"text":"From every suburbia, and every hood"}]},{"cues":[{"time":123950,"text":"‘Cause the only God of language is\nthe one recorded in the Genesis"}]},{"cues":[{"time":127503,"text":"Of this world saying “it is good\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":129220,"text":"So I may not always come before you"},{"time":131791,"text":"with excellency of speech"}]},{"cues":[{"time":133185,"text":"But do not judge me by my language and assume"}]},{"cues":[{"time":135716,"text":"That I’m too ignorant to teach"}]},{"cues":[{"time":137235,"text":"‘Cause I speak three tongues"}]},{"cues":[{"time":138785,"text":"One for each:"}]},{"cues":[{"time":139933,"text":"Home, school and friends"}]},{"cues":[{"time":141678,"text":"I’m a tri-lingual orator"}]},{"cues":[{"time":143882,"text":"Sometimes I’m consistent with my language now"}]},{"cues":[{"time":145851,"text":"Then switch it up so I don’t bore later"}]},{"cues":[{"time":147810,"text":"Sometimes I fight back two tongues"}]},{"cues":[{"time":149687,"text":"While I use the other one in the classroom"}]},{"cues":[{"time":151622,"text":"And when I mistakenly mix them up"}]},{"cues":[{"time":153547,"text":"I feel crazy like … I’m cooking in the bathroom"}]},{"cues":[{"time":157040,"text":"I know that I had to borrow your language"},{"time":161632,"text":"because mines was stolen"}]},{"cues":[{"time":164477,"text":"But you can’t expect me to speak your history wholly"},{"time":168377,"text":"while mines is broken"}]},{"cues":[{"time":169879,"text":"These words are spoken"}]},{"cues":[{"time":171398,"text":"By someone who is simply fed up with"},{"time":173705,"text":"the Eurocentric ideals of this season"}]},{"cues":[{"time":176325,"text":"And the reason I speak a composite\nversion of your language"}]},{"cues":[{"time":179808,"text":"Is because mines was raped\naway along with my history"}]},{"cues":[{"time":183560,"text":"I speak broken English so the\nprofusing gashes can remind us"}]},{"cues":[{"time":187790,"text":"That our current state is not a mystery"}]},{"cues":[{"time":190050,"text":"I’m so tired of the negative images\nthat are driving my people mad"}]},{"cues":[{"time":195258,"text":"So unless you’ve seen it rob\na bank stop calling my hair bad"}]},{"cues":[{"time":199501,"text":"I’m so sick of this nonsensical racial disparity"}]},{"cues":[{"time":203157,"text":"So don’t call it good unless your hair is known"},{"time":205710,"text":"for donating to charity"}]},{"cues":[{"time":207255,"text":"As much as has been raped away from our people"}]},{"cues":[{"time":212182,"text":"How can you expect me to treat\ntheir imprint on your language"}]},{"cues":[{"time":216121,"text":"As anything less than equal"}]},{"cues":[{"time":218735,"text":"Let there be no confusion"}]},{"cues":[{"time":220607,"text":"Let there be no hesitation"}]},{"cues":[{"time":222421,"text":"This is not a promotion of ignorance"}]},{"cues":[{"time":224485,"text":"This is a linguistic celebration"}]},{"cues":[{"time":227930,"text":"That’s why I put \"tri-lingual\" on my last job application"}]},{"cues":[{"time":233009,"text":"I can help to diversify your consumer market"},{"time":235740,"text":"is all I wanted them to know"}]},{"cues":[{"time":237372,"text":"And when they call me for the interview"},{"time":239105,"text":"I’ll be more than happy to show that"}]},{"cues":[{"time":240615,"text":"I can say:"}]},{"cues":[{"time":241350,"text":"“What’s good”"}]},{"cues":[{"time":242563,"text":"“Whatagwan”"}]},{"cues":[{"time":243548,"text":"And of course …“Hello”"}]},{"cues":[{"time":246452,"text":"Because I’m “articulate”"}]},{"cues":[{"time":249126,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":250899,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}